["addation_086b4870b60812ce"] = "Let\'s face it. Goats smell bad, they really do. Hauling a dozen or so of them in a helicopter means you will smell bad too. To spare your fellow heisters a load of agony, head straight to the shower after any goat-hauling shenanigans.", 
