["addation_49c9f4cf643e7001"] = "The Election Day Heist is the third free heist update to PAYDAY 2. It allows heisters to take a new contract from the corrupt politician the Elephant called the Election Day heist. Heisters are to help the Elephant get his man Bob McKendrick into the Mayor\'s office by locating the voting machines. The heisters then need to hack the machines to swing the vote. Finally, heisters need to make sure no suspicion falls on The Elephant. Along with the new Election Day heist comes a major stealth update. The Chimano Custom pistol is also added for free to anyone who joins the Official PAYDAY 2 Community group on Steam. Last but not least, players can enjoy 10 new achievements to unlock.", 
