["addation_aa41ce861ea8a6db"] = "The Gage Historical Pack DLC is the 12th DLC pack for PAYDAY 2 and adds an array of historical weapons to the Payday Gang.$NL;$NL;One sniper rifle, one pistol, one submachine gun, one light machine gun, four new melee weapons, the bayonet feature and a host of weapon mods so you can nostalgia hard. Four old, dusty masks have also been added with patterns and materials to personalize them further. 5 new achievements have made their way to see if you are a real man or a fleeing coward.", 
