["addation_9dd631e46552299f"] = "Nationality: American$NL;Age: 40s$NL;$NL;John Wick is a quiet and calm former hitman. He has a seemingly ageless physique, probably from his background as a boxer. John and Chains know each other from before as they used to be in the military together.$NL;$NL;After having gone dark, John recently resurfaced and helped Chains out of a delicate situation. In return, John told Chains he was in need of a crew. How could Chains say no to an old friend?", 
